WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.000
♪ Who's gonna help when the danger overwhelms ♪

00:03.000 --> 00:05.000
♪ And the mysteries are piled high? ♪

00:05.000 --> 00:07.000
♪ Who's gonna be around, never gonna let you down ♪

00:07.000 --> 00:09.000
♪ When you're on a wild ride? ♪

00:09.000 --> 00:10.000
♪ Your friends are always by your side ♪

00:10.000 --> 00:15.000
♪ It's Craig of the Creek, he's gonna save the day ♪

00:15.000 --> 00:19.000
♪ It's Craig of the Creek, he's gonna save the day ♪

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
♪ It's Craig of the Creek ♪

00:24.000 --> 00:25.000
[ Imitates explosions ]

00:26.000 --> 00:27.000
Oh, no!

00:27.000 --> 00:29.000
Craig: Now back on the road.

00:29.000 --> 00:31.000
Now spin cycle.

00:31.000 --> 00:33.000
[ Imitates revving ]

00:33.000 --> 00:35.000
Knight and Steed have returned!

00:35.000 --> 00:37.000
[ Whinnies ]

00:37.000 --> 00:40.000
Maney and I found Sailor Boy in the far west of the creek,

00:40.000 --> 00:43.000
his jacket in the clutches of a vicious thorn bush.

00:44.000 --> 00:45.000
Sailor Boy survived.

00:45.000 --> 00:47.000
The bush did not. That's cool.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
We were playing with the racecars,

00:49.000 --> 00:52.000
but the batteries died, so now they're JP-powered.

00:52.000 --> 00:53.000
Oh.

00:53.000 --> 00:55.000
Turbo jump!

00:55.000 --> 00:57.000
[ Whinnies ]

00:57.000 --> 00:59.000
[ Sighs ]

00:59.000 --> 01:02.000
P-P-Perfect parkin'!

01:03.000 --> 01:04.000
Oh, hello, there, Maney.

01:04.000 --> 01:07.000
Uh, uh... H-Hey, JP. I, uh...

01:07.000 --> 01:08.000
Hmm?

01:08.000 --> 01:11.000
I think I -- I like, um...

01:11.000 --> 01:13.000
You like what?

01:13.000 --> 01:15.000
I-I-I like horses!

01:15.000 --> 01:17.000
I think you'd make a great horse! [ Gasps ]

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
[ Whinnies ]

01:20.000 --> 01:24.000
Wow. Nobody's ever told me I'd be a good anythin' before.

01:24.000 --> 01:25.000
Huh.

01:25.000 --> 01:29.000
[ All neighing ]

01:29.000 --> 01:31.000
Okay, now that we've all warmed up our horse vocals,

01:31.000 --> 01:33.000
I hope you're all ready for Trot Day!

01:34.000 --> 01:36.000
Oh! I love trotting!

01:36.000 --> 01:38.000
Oh, I'm so ready to trot!

01:38.000 --> 01:40.000
Yes, Melissa, we know.

01:40.000 --> 01:42.000
I want to see some high knee kicks today, girls.

01:42.000 --> 01:44.000
I'm lookin' at you, Marie.

01:44.000 --> 01:47.000
Oh, yeah, sure, but I've decided I'm a pretty old horse,

01:47.000 --> 01:51.000
so my trot may look more like a walk, like most of the time.

01:51.000 --> 01:53.000
-Maney! -JP?

01:53.000 --> 01:56.000
JP, w-what are you doing here?

01:56.000 --> 01:57.000
What you said got me thinkin'.

01:57.000 --> 02:00.000
I looked real deep inside myself and you were right.

02:00.000 --> 02:03.000
I was born to be a horse. Check it.

02:03.000 --> 02:05.000
[ Grunting ]

02:05.000 --> 02:06.000
[ Gasps ]

02:06.000 --> 02:08.000
Mackenzie: Neigh-excuse me?!

02:08.000 --> 02:09.000
[ All whinny ]

02:09.000 --> 02:11.000
What are  you doing here?

02:11.000 --> 02:13.000
I invited him, Mackenzie.

02:13.000 --> 02:15.000
JP wants to be a horse like us.

02:16.000 --> 02:17.000
Really?

02:17.000 --> 02:20.000
This isn't a game, you know. It's a lifestyle.

02:20.000 --> 02:22.000
Many have tried to be a horse,

02:22.000 --> 02:24.000
but few have the heart... of a horse.

02:25.000 --> 02:29.000
Yeah. Kids normally get tired of being a horse, but not us.

02:29.000 --> 02:31.000
Not...us.

02:31.000 --> 02:32.000
If you want to be a Horse Girl,

02:32.000 --> 02:35.000
then you got to have horse in your blood!

02:35.000 --> 02:38.000
Are you willing to show us your blood?!

02:38.000 --> 02:40.000
Eek! Wait! Please!

02:40.000 --> 02:42.000
Can't we just give him a chance?

02:42.000 --> 02:43.000
Yeah. I'm serious about this.

02:43.000 --> 02:47.000
I'll do whatever it takes to embody the equine lifestyle.

02:47.000 --> 02:49.000
[ Snorts ] Fine.

02:49.000 --> 02:51.000
I guess you can trot with us for a while.

02:51.000 --> 02:52.000
Yeah! Yay!

02:52.000 --> 02:53.000
What's a trot?

02:54.000 --> 02:56.000
I suppose you two wanna be horses, too?

02:56.000 --> 02:59.000
Oh, nah, we're -- we're just along for the ride.

02:59.000 --> 03:01.000
This is bumpy!

03:01.000 --> 03:04.000
To be a horse, you have to be powerful.

03:04.000 --> 03:06.000
But also graceful.

03:06.000 --> 03:09.000
-Yeah! -Yee!

03:09.000 --> 03:13.000
And most importantly, you have to answer the call of adventure!

03:13.000 --> 03:15.000
[ All neighing ]

03:15.000 --> 03:18.000
♪♪

03:18.000 --> 03:20.000
Whoa. JP. Whoa!

03:20.000 --> 03:22.000
Weeeee!

03:22.000 --> 03:24.000
Ugh, not majestic.

03:24.000 --> 03:27.000
I'm okay. Craig broke my fall.

03:27.000 --> 03:30.000
[ Chuckles ] JP is so funny.

03:30.000 --> 03:32.000
Horses aren't supposed to be funny.

03:32.000 --> 03:33.000
Rodeo clowns are funny.

03:33.000 --> 03:36.000
And horses kick them in the face!

03:36.000 --> 03:37.000
Okay, snack time.

03:37.000 --> 03:40.000
I got the choco roll hookup for all of us.

03:40.000 --> 03:42.000
Coo? Oh, Mortimer.

03:42.000 --> 03:44.000
I'm sorry. I didn't actually pack anything for you.

03:44.000 --> 03:46.000
[ Bird screeches ]

03:46.000 --> 03:49.000
Aw, yeah, I'm so hungry I could eat a horse.

03:49.000 --> 03:51.000
Mackenzie: Ah-hehehem!

03:51.000 --> 03:53.000
First of all, how dare you.

03:53.000 --> 03:56.000
Second of all, horses don't have hands, they have hooves.

03:56.000 --> 03:58.000
Oh, uh...

03:58.000 --> 04:04.000
♪♪

04:04.000 --> 04:06.000
Oop! [ Squish! ]

04:06.000 --> 04:08.000
[ Grunts ]

04:08.000 --> 04:16.000
♪♪

04:16.000 --> 04:19.000
All right, it's time for dressage practice.

04:16.000 --> 04:19.000
Yes!

04:19.000 --> 04:23.000
Oh, good. I'm really good at puttin' on pants.

04:19.000 --> 04:23.000
[ Chuckles ]

04:23.000 --> 04:26.000
Dressage is like a dance competition for horses.

04:26.000 --> 04:28.000
And Mackenzie is incredible.

04:30.000 --> 04:31.000
Music!

04:31.000 --> 04:33.000
Marie. Your hooves.

04:33.000 --> 04:35.000
Just imagine my hand is a tiny horse

04:35.000 --> 04:38.000
and I'm using my tiny hooves.

04:38.000 --> 04:42.000
♪♪

04:42.000 --> 04:43.000
[ Gasps ]

04:43.000 --> 04:47.000
♪♪

04:47.000 --> 04:49.000
I have to say, Kelsey,

04:49.000 --> 04:52.000
this is one of the best dressage routines I've ever seen!

04:52.000 --> 04:53.000
That's right, Craig.

04:53.000 --> 04:55.000
It's also the only dressage routine

04:55.000 --> 04:56.000
I have ever seen.

04:57.000 --> 04:59.000
So, is Maney your mom-given name?

04:59.000 --> 05:02.000
No, it's short for Mangerine.

05:02.000 --> 05:03.000
Oh, I like that.

05:03.000 --> 05:06.000
♪♪

05:06.000 --> 05:08.000
Yeah! Whoo-hoo!

05:08.000 --> 05:11.000
Melissa! Horses don't scream.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.000
Maney, what did you think

05:12.000 --> 05:14.000
of that trot-halt-trot that I added?

05:14.000 --> 05:17.000
[ Giggles ] When do you think

05:14.000 --> 05:17.000
my horse teeth'll come in?

05:17.000 --> 05:18.000
Hmph!

05:18.000 --> 05:20.000
Can I go next?!

05:20.000 --> 05:23.000
No, let's see what our new  neigh-bor can do.

05:23.000 --> 05:26.000
[ Snorts ] Uh, mehehe?

05:26.000 --> 05:28.000
♪♪

05:28.000 --> 05:30.000
This should be rich.

05:30.000 --> 05:32.000
Uh, I don't know how to do any of that fancy footwork,

05:32.000 --> 05:35.000
but I do know this lil' thing.

05:35.000 --> 05:37.000
Hit it!

05:37.000 --> 05:38.000
Now, this is a dance I made up

05:38.000 --> 05:41.000
when I had a bee stuck in my shirt.

05:41.000 --> 05:44.000
It goes a little something like this.

05:44.000 --> 05:47.000
♪ Now, stick out your arms like you've got long sleeves ♪

05:47.000 --> 05:49.000
♪ Wave 'em around just like me ♪

05:49.000 --> 05:50.000
♪ Don't be shy, just get funky ♪

05:51.000 --> 05:53.000
♪ And do the JP ♪

05:53.000 --> 05:55.000
-Come on, guys! -Yeah!

05:55.000 --> 05:57.000
What? ♪ A-wiggle-wiggle-wiggle ♪

05:57.000 --> 06:01.000
♪ That's right, do the JP ♪

06:01.000 --> 06:03.000
♪ So you're not a JP, you're a Kyle ♪

06:03.000 --> 06:06.000
♪ That's okay, just wave your arms freestyle ♪

06:06.000 --> 06:08.000
Yeah.

06:08.000 --> 06:12.000
I am movin' all over the place.

06:12.000 --> 06:14.000
♪ Do the JP ♪

06:14.000 --> 06:16.000
Come on, everyone watching at home.

06:16.000 --> 06:18.000
Get up and dance along.

06:18.000 --> 06:20.000
It's real easy to...

06:20.000 --> 06:22.000
♪ Do the JP ♪

06:23.000 --> 06:24.000
Yeah! Yes!

06:24.000 --> 06:27.000
That is not how horses dance!

06:27.000 --> 06:30.000
♪♪

06:30.000 --> 06:32.000
I knew you'd be a great horse.

06:32.000 --> 06:35.000
T-That means a lot comin' from a --

06:35.000 --> 06:37.000
a genuine equine such as yourself.

06:37.000 --> 06:39.000
[ Chuckles ]

06:39.000 --> 06:41.000
I feel like I messed up, though, a couple times back there.

06:41.000 --> 06:43.000
I mean, Mackenzie seems kinda mad.

06:43.000 --> 06:45.000
You're just different.

06:45.000 --> 06:48.000
Wild! Untamed!

06:48.000 --> 06:50.000
Unbroken.

06:51.000 --> 06:52.000
[ Whispers ] Should we leave?

06:52.000 --> 06:54.000
[ Whispers ] Don't dismount. You'll ruin the moment.

06:55.000 --> 06:57.000
I've wanted to hang out with you for some time now.

06:58.000 --> 07:00.000
I-I-I'm happy I fin-finally can.

07:00.000 --> 07:02.000
Yeah, this is so fun.

07:02.000 --> 07:04.000
I wanna do this every day.

07:04.000 --> 07:08.000
[ Humming "Do the JP" ]

07:10.000 --> 07:13.000
♪♪

07:13.000 --> 07:15.000
I feel great! I slept standin' up last night!

07:15.000 --> 07:17.000
Hold your horses!

07:17.000 --> 07:19.000
You've had your fun, JP.

07:19.000 --> 07:21.000
But if you want to keep galloping with the herd,

07:21.000 --> 07:23.000
you'll have to go through the horse rite of passage --

07:23.000 --> 07:25.000
the horse course.

07:25.000 --> 07:26.000
[ Both gasp ]

07:26.000 --> 07:29.000
Mackenzie, JP isn't ready for the horse course.

07:29.000 --> 07:30.000
It takes weeks of training

07:30.000 --> 07:33.000
and -- and he's only been a horse for one day.

07:33.000 --> 07:35.000
I don't know if Marie has even --

07:33.000 --> 07:35.000
Shh!

07:35.000 --> 07:37.000
You don't have to do this.

07:37.000 --> 07:41.000
The course is hard, even for a stallion like yourself.

07:41.000 --> 07:42.000
Those are the rules,

07:42.000 --> 07:44.000
but JP can always tuck his pony tail between his legs

07:44.000 --> 07:47.000
and go home, that's if he even has a tail.

07:47.000 --> 07:51.000
I accept the challenge.

07:51.000 --> 07:52.000
Craig: Here we are, Kelsey.

07:52.000 --> 07:54.000
It's a beautiful day for a horse course.

07:54.000 --> 07:57.000
Yes, Craig, but this test ain't no trot in the meadow.

07:57.000 --> 08:00.000
The jumps are high and the stakes are even higher.

08:00.000 --> 08:02.000
The horse course starts here.

08:02.000 --> 08:04.000
First, you must execute a dainty hop over the small jump,

08:04.000 --> 08:07.000
then a trot through the puddle, pay respects to the dignitaries,

08:07.000 --> 08:11.000
and finally, clear a totally regulation-sized high jump.

08:11.000 --> 08:12.000
Finish the course without failing a jump,

08:12.000 --> 08:14.000
and you'll officially be one of us.

08:14.000 --> 08:17.000
You have until Melissa finishes drawing a horse with her mouth.

08:17.000 --> 08:19.000
So be fast 'cause she's got it down to a science.

08:19.000 --> 08:22.000
I know you can do this, JP. Good luck.

08:22.000 --> 08:24.000
Ready, Melissa?

08:24.000 --> 08:25.000
[ Muffled ] Ready!

08:25.000 --> 08:26.000
Go!

08:26.000 --> 08:28.000
Whoo-hoo! Yeah! JP!

08:28.000 --> 08:31.000
And he's off to a strong start!

08:31.000 --> 08:32.000
You know, it's hard to believe

08:32.000 --> 08:35.000
he only became a horse yesterday, Craig.

08:35.000 --> 08:37.000
Wow! So elegant.

08:37.000 --> 08:39.000
So untamed.

08:39.000 --> 08:40.000
That was hardly a trot!

08:41.000 --> 08:43.000
[ Grunting ]

08:44.000 --> 08:47.000
M'lord, m'lady, m'baby.

08:48.000 --> 08:49.000
What are all those dots?

08:49.000 --> 08:50.000
[ Muffled ] Spots!

08:50.000 --> 08:52.000
Melissa, it doesn't need details!

08:52.000 --> 08:54.000
He's entering the home stretch, folks.

08:54.000 --> 08:56.000
He's just got to clear the final high jump.

08:56.000 --> 08:58.000
♪♪

08:58.000 --> 09:00.000
Hurry up, Melissa!

09:01.000 --> 09:02.000
[ All gasp ]

09:02.000 --> 09:04.000
Wow.

09:04.000 --> 09:06.000
♪♪

09:06.000 --> 09:07.000
[ Grunts ]

09:07.000 --> 09:10.000
[ All gasp ]

09:10.000 --> 09:12.000
JP! JP, can you get up?

09:13.000 --> 09:15.000
No. His horse leg is broken!

09:15.000 --> 09:16.000
We have to put him down like in the movies.

09:16.000 --> 09:18.000
Melissa, no, not again.

09:18.000 --> 09:21.000
Well, he can't be a horse anymore anyway.

09:21.000 --> 09:22.000
He lost the course!

09:22.000 --> 09:23.000
Mackenzie: No, he didn't.

09:23.000 --> 09:26.000
Because I...I sabotaged it!

09:26.000 --> 09:27.000
[ All gasp ]

09:27.000 --> 09:29.000
I just wanted him to fail the course!

09:29.000 --> 09:30.000
I didn't think he'd get hurt!

09:31.000 --> 09:33.000
[ Grunting, snorting ]

09:33.000 --> 09:36.000
JP gave everything he could to be a horse like us

09:36.000 --> 09:38.000
and this is how you treat him?!

09:38.000 --> 09:40.000
I'm sorry, okay?! I-I just --

09:40.000 --> 09:41.000
You just what?!

09:41.000 --> 09:43.000
I just -- Everyone was having more fun

09:43.000 --> 09:45.000
doing horse stuff JP's way.

09:45.000 --> 09:47.000
I was worried that if he joined us,

09:47.000 --> 09:49.000
he'd change our horse way of life forever.

09:49.000 --> 09:52.000
And then you wouldn't need me anymore.

09:52.000 --> 09:55.000
Oh, Mackenzie, of course we need you.

09:55.000 --> 09:58.000
We wouldn't be The Horse Girls without you.

09:58.000 --> 10:00.000
Really? Yeah.

10:00.000 --> 10:03.000
I mean, sure, you can be bossy sometimes,

10:03.000 --> 10:04.000
but I know it's just because

10:04.000 --> 10:06.000
you want to bring out our fullest potential.

10:06.000 --> 10:08.000
Maney, Maney, I'm sorry,

10:09.000 --> 10:11.000
but I don't think I wanna be a horse anymore.

10:11.000 --> 10:14.000
But I thought you were having fun as a horse.

10:14.000 --> 10:16.000
I thought we were gonna be horses together.

10:16.000 --> 10:19.000
Of course I had fun. I was hangin' out with you!

10:19.000 --> 10:21.000
But I don't belong in the meadow.

10:21.000 --> 10:23.000
My heart's just not as into it as you guys.

10:23.000 --> 10:26.000
And let's be honest, you got the best horses right here.

10:27.000 --> 10:31.000
Besides, I realize now that I'm neither boy nor horse.

10:31.000 --> 10:33.000
I'm...a truck!

10:33.000 --> 10:37.000
My hooves be wheels! My tail, a tail pipe!

10:37.000 --> 10:39.000
My farts -- terrible for the ozone layer.

10:39.000 --> 10:42.000
But I hope that we can still ride together

10:39.000 --> 10:42.000
every once in a while.

10:42.000 --> 10:43.000
[ Snorts ]

10:44.000 --> 10:46.000
Of course we can.

10:46.000 --> 10:48.000
All right, fellas.

10:48.000 --> 10:51.000
It's a long drive home, and I'm gonna need a push.

10:51.000 --> 10:52.000
[ Both groan ]

10:52.000 --> 10:54.000
Group nuzzle!

10:55.000 --> 10:57.000
[ All whinny ]

10:58.000 --> 11:01.000
[ Both grunting ]

11:01.000 --> 11:04.000
♪ When it's time to go to bed ♪

11:04.000 --> 11:09.000
♪ I know I don't have to feel alone ♪

11:09.000 --> 11:12.000
♪ 'Cause I'll see you tomorrow ♪

11:12.000 --> 11:13.000
♪ At the creek ♪

11:14.000 --> 11:16.000
Just like I drew it.
